sub_title: Finance student aspiring to create globally
summary:
I'm now pursuing a bachelor's degree in international business with a finance major. During my studies working in intercultural teams, my soft skills have greatly improved, especially as a leader. It has also strengthened my analytical abilities, financial skills, and critical thinking. 

I pursued a minor focused on "Doing Business in China". It emphasized on supply chain (finance), Mandarin, culture, and business etiquette.

My history consist of a degree in marketing graduated cum laude. Both inland and overseas, internships with firms like Toponderzoek, Mijnwerkplek, and Mijnvorm have utilized the expertise I gained throughout my studies. In addition, it resulted in my own start-up, which has successfully been handed to a new partner.
